;; **
;;; Grape Path Expressions use Neo4J Cipher Syntax. They consist of a series of _segments_, where each segment has the form 
;;; 
;;; * -[exp]- (for an traversal in any direction)
;;; * -[exp]-> (for traversal in forwar direction)
;;; * <-[exp]- (traversal in backwar direction)
