;;; {"type":"html","content":"<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"155\" height=\"186\" alt=\"\" />","value":"#object[java.awt.image.BufferedImage 0x68aae518 \"BufferedImage@68aae518: type = 6 ColorModel: #pixelBits = 32 numComponents = 4 color space = java.awt.color.ICC_ColorSpace@3ebd1ea7 transparency = 3 has alpha = true isAlphaPre = false ByteInterleavedRaster: width = 155 height = 186 #numDataElements 4 dataOff[0] = 3\"]"}
;; <=

